    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "healing? how is there even anything left to heal? it's not just a setback. it's like the person i was is actually dead. when people look at me they don't see a person, they see a mistake. there is no \"new direction\" when you've lost the only version of yourself that actually mattered. it feels like the world has just decided i'm done.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
