      "role": "user",
      "content": "exactly. it's like you're just watching the credits roll on a movie you didn't even want to finish. everyone's moved on, the world is still turning, but i'm just stuck in this wreckage. i don't see the point in trying to glue the pieces back together when the whole thing is fundamentally ruined. it just feels so heavy... like there's no real way to make it right again.",
